    "<html><head/><body><p style='white-space:pre'>Add CBR, CBZ, CB7 or PDF file to queue.</p></body></html>": "<html><head/><body><p style='white-space:pre'>Añadir CBR, CBZ, CB7 o PDF.</p></body></html>",
    "Add input file(s)": "Añadir archivos",
    "<html><head/><body><p style='white-space:pre'>Add directory containing JPG, PNG or GIF files to queue.<br/><span style=\" font-weight:600;\">CBR, CBZ and CB7 files inside will not be processed!</span></p></body></html>": "<html><head/><body><p style='white-space:pre'>Añadir carpeta (JPG, PNG o GIF).<br/><span style=\" font-weight:600;\">¡Omitirá CBR, CBZ y CB7!</span></p></body></html>",
    "Add input folder(s)": "Añadir carpetas",
    "<html><head/><body><p style='white-space:pre'>Output format.</p></body></html>": "<html><head/><body><p style='white-space:pre'>Formato de salida.</p></body></html>",
    "<html><head/><body><p>Double click on source to open it in metadata editor.</p></body></html>": "<html><head/><body><p>Doble click para abrir el editor de metadatos.</p></body></html>",
    "<html><head/><body><p>Warning: chunk size greater than default may cause<br/>performance/battery issues, especially on older devices.</p></body></html>": "<html><head/><body><p>Aviso: un tamaño alto puede<br/>dar problemas de batería en disp. antiguos.</p></body></html>",
    "Chunk size MB:": "Tamaño MB:",
