    "Inter-panel crop": "Recorte viñetas",
    "<html><head/><body><p><span style=\" font-weight:600; text-decoration: underline;\">Unchecked - Split<br/></span>Double page spreads will be cut into two separate pages.</p><p><span style=\" font-weight:600; text-decoration: underline;\">Indeterminate - Split and rotate<br/></span>Double page spreads will be displayed twice. First split and then rotated. </p><p><span style=\" font-weight:600; text-decoration: underline;\">Checked - Rotate<br/></span>Double page spreads will be rotated.</p></body></html>": "<html><head/><body><p><span style=\" font-weight:600; text-decoration: underline;\">Sin marcar<br/></span>Cortar mitad.</p><p><span style=\" font-weight:600; text-decoration: underline;\">Gris - Cortar y rotar<br/></span>Pone primero mitad y luego completa doblada. </p><p><span style=\" font-weight:600; text-decoration: underline;\">Marcado - Rotar<br/></span>Verla recostada doblar.</p></body></html>",
    "Spread splitter": "Cortar doble pág",
